{"word":"Revenge","slug":"revenge","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Revenge</b> Forbidden<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=19&verse=18'>Lev 19:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=24&verse=29'>Pro 24:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=12&verse=17'>Rom 12:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=12&verse=19'>Rom 12:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=52&chapter=5&verse=15'>1Th 5:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=3&verse=9'>1Pe 3:9</a><br/> Jesus an example of forbearing<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=2&verse=23'>1Pe 2:23</a><br/> Rebuked by Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=9&verse=55'>Luk 9:55</a><br/> Inconsistent with a Christian spirit<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=9&verse=55'>Luk 9:55</a><br/> Proceeds from a spiteful heart<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=25&verse=15'>Eze 25:15</a><br/> Punishment for<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=25&verse=17'>Eze 25:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=1&verse=12'>Amo 1:12</a><br/> Exemplified:<br/> - By Simeon and Levi<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=34&verse=25'>Gen 34:25</a> <br/> - By Samson<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=15&verse=8'>Jdg 15:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=16&verse=30'>Jdg 16:30</a> <br/> - By Joab<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=3&verse=27'>2Sa 3:27</a> <br/> - By Absalom<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=13&verse=29'>2Sa 13:29</a> <br/> - By Jezebel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=19&verse=2'>1Ki 19:2</a> <br/> - By Ahab<br/> <a href='https://ww